      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the ideal synergy of performance and sophisticated maintenance. The exterior retains a striking presence with a deep, glossy finish, showing only the slight character marks consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the seats provide firm support with minimal wear, and every feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the intuitive navigation\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the car has been treated to a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule, resulting in a powertrain that is both responsive and whisper-quiet. The suspension remains tight, offering a smooth, confident ride that feels as though it just left the showroom a few years ago. Included with the sale are comprehensive service records and two sets of keys, providing the next owner with complete peace of mind and a turn-key driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
